{"questionId":"13810259","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The cost of a journey on the different boat routes is given in the following table; all prices are given in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>USD</mi></math>. The cost of a journey is the same in either direction between two ports.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/f8c5fd340751d010c11ffcea6632ac8f6a9ba4a5.png\"></p>\n<p>Sofia wants to make a trip where she travels on each of the boat routes at least once, beginning and ending at port <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Given that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">P</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>5</mn></mtd><mtd><mi>a</mi></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>5</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>5</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd><mtd><mi>a</mi></mtd><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>5</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>,&nbsp;find the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd